"         Severe wasting",
"        </span>",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"     </table>",
"    </center>",
"    <br/>",
"    &nbsp;",
"    <br/>",
"    <span class=\"medCalcFontOneBold\">",
"     Notes",
"    </span>",
"    <ul class=\"medCalcFontOne\">",
"     <li>",
"      Moderate malnutrition is defined as moderate stunting or wasting. Severe malnutrition is defined as severe stunting",
"or severe wasting, or edematous malnutrition. Patients with edematous malnutrition (Kwashiorkor) should be considered to",
"have severe malnutrition even if stunting or wasting z-scores are not in the severe range.",
"     </li>",
"     <li>",
"      This calculator uses measured recumbent Length for infants and toddlers from birth through 24 months of age,",
"and is not valid for standing height.",
"     </li>",
"    </ul>",
"    <br/>",
"    &nbsp;",
